      <title>新西兰国庆节抗议者为原住民权利示威</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-national-day-protesters-demonstrate-indigenous-rights-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，大约 600 名抗议者游行到怀唐伊镇新西兰建国文件签署地，官方庆祝活动与针对威胁原住民权利的拟议政府政策的抗议活动同时展开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-national-day-protesters-demonstrate-indigenous-rights-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 23:15:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总理称中国法院对澳大利亚作家缓刑的判决“令人愤慨”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-courts-suspended-death-sentence-australian-writer-an-outrage-pm-says-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞周二表示，北京法院以间谍罪判处澳大利亚作家杨恒均死刑缓期执行，这“令人愤慨”，并誓言将继续努力争取杨恒均获释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-courts-suspended-death-sentence-australian-writer-an-outrage-pm-says-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:40:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
